      <fieldvalue value="<div class=&quot;content_para&quot;><p><em>Guideline Authors</em>: Hans D. Katzberg, MD; Ahmir H. Khan, MD; Yuen T. So, MD, PhD</p>
<p><em>Therapeutics and Technology Assessment Subcommittee Members (2007-2009)</em>: Janis M. Miyasaki, MD, MEd, FAAN (<em>Co-Chair</em>); Yuen T. So, MD, PhD (<em>Co-Chair</em>); Richard M. Camicioli, MD; Vinay Chaudhry, MD, FAAN; Richard M. Dubinsky, MD, MPH, FAAN; Cynthia L. Harden, MD; Cheryl Jaigobin, MD; Irene L. Katzan, MD; Barbara S. Koppel, MD, FAAN; James C. Stevens, MD, FAAN (Ex-Officio); William H. Theodore, MD, FAAN. </p></div>"/>
